        <div n="540-39LD" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-1"><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><hi rend="display-initial">W</hi>ITH favours, and fortune fastidiously blest,</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-2"> He's loud in his laugh, he's coarse in his jest,</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-3"> Of favour and fortune unmerited vain,</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-4"> A sharper in trifles, a dupe in the main,</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-5"> Atchieving of nothing, still promising wonders,</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-6"> By dint of experience improving in blunders;</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-7"> Oppressing true merit, exalting the base,</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-8"> And selling his country to purchase a p────;</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-9"> A jobber of stocks, by retailing false news,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-10"> A prater at court in the stile of the stews;</l><l n="11" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-11"> Of virtue and worth by profession a giber</l><l n="12" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-12"> Of S────s and J────s the bully and briber:</l><l n="13" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-13"> Tho' I name not the wretch, you'll guess who I mean,</l><l n="14" xml:id="spp-540-39LD-line-14" rend="flush right"> 'Tis the cur-dog of <hi rend="underline">Britain</hi> and spaniel of <hi rend="underline">Spain</hi>.<hi rend="underline">J.C.</hi>──Seven's the main.540-39LD   </l></lg></div>
